{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/basic-javascript/use-the-conditional-ternary-operator","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"basic-javascript","demoType":null,"title":"Tumia opereta ya kikokotoo cha masharti cha pande tatu","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>&#x3C;Uslovni operator</dfn>, poznat i kao <dfn>ternarni operator</dfn>, može se koristiti kao jednolinijski <code>if-else</code> izraz.</p>\n<p>Sintaksa je <code>a ? b : c</code>, gde je <code>a</code> uslov, <code>b</code> je kod koji se izvršava kada uslov vrati <code>true</code>, a <code>c</code> je kod koji se izvršava kada uslov vrati <code>false</code>.</p>\n<p>Sledeća funkcija koristi naredbu <code>if/else</code> da proveri uslov:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-js\">function findGreater(a, b) {\n  if(a > b) {\n    return \"a is greater\";\n  }\n  else {\n    return \"b is greater or equal\";\n  }\n}\n</code></pre>\n<p>Ovo se može prepisati korišćenjem uslovnog operatora:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-js\">function findGreater(a, b) {\n  return a > b ? \"a is greater\" : \"b is greater or equal\";\n}\n</code></pre>\n</section>","id":"587d7b7e367417b2b2512b24","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"<section id=\"instructions\">\n<p>Koristi uslovni operator u funkciji <code>checkEqual</code> da proveri da li su dva broja jednaka. Funkcija treba da vrati string <code>Equal</code> ili string <code>Not Equal</code>.</p>\n</section>","notes":null,"challengeType":1,"helpCategory":"JavaScript","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":301181,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/basic-javascript/use-the-conditional-ternary-operator"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"function checkEqual(a, b) {\n\n}\n\ncheckEqual(1, 2);","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["script.js"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p><code>checkEqual</code> inapaswa kutumia opereta ya masharti</p>","testString":"assert(/.+?\\s*?\\?\\s*?.+?\\s*?:\\s*?.+?/.test(__helpers.removeJSComments(code)));"},{"text":"<p><code>checkEqual(1, 2)</code> treba da vrati string <code>Not Equal</code></p>","testString":"assert(checkEqual(1, 2) === 'Not Equal');"},{"text":"<p><code>checkEqual(1, 1)</code> treba da vrati string <code>Equal</code></p>","testString":"assert(checkEqual(1, 1) === 'Equal');"},{"text":"<p><code>checkEqual(1, -1)</code> treba da vrati string <code>Not Equal</code></p>","testString":"assert(checkEqual(1, -1) === 'Not Equal');"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/#basic-javascript","dashedName":"use-the-conditional-ternary-operator","certification":"javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures","disableLoopProtectTests":false,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"basic-javascript","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/basic-javascript/use-multiple-conditional-ternary-operators","prevChallengePath":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/basic-javascript/use-the-parseint-function-with-a-radix","id":"587d7b7e367417b2b2512b24","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":1,"challengeFiles":[{"name":"script","ext":"js","contents":"function rangeOfNumbers(startNum, endNum) {\n  if (endNum - startNum === 0) {\n    return [startNum];\n  } else {\n    const numbers = rangeOfNumbers(startNum, endNum - 1);\n    numbers.push(endNum);\n    return numbers;\n  }\n}","history":["script.js"],"fileKey":"scriptjs"}]}},"id":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/basic-javascript/use-the-conditional-ternary-operator"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3858520367"],"slicesMap":{}}